The heat equation is
$$
-\nabla\cdot(\kappa\nabla u)=0,~~u|_{C_0}=20,~~u|_{C_1}=100.
$$
~~~freefem
solve a(u, v)
  = int2d(Th)(kappa*(dx(u)*dx(v) + dy(u)*dy(v)))
  + on(C0, u=20)
  + on(C1, u=100);
plot(u, value=true, wait=1, fill=true);
~~~

